8T15:46:53.000Z","msg":"笑撚咗，兩個二打六係樂壇先驅，你同你老母都係樂壇先驅啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T19:04:27.000Z","msg":"唔識字? 內文都冇提到佢哋係「樂壇」先驅<br />\n高嘉瑜係台灣立委<br />\n<br />\n不過我個人都認同HOCC係香港樂壇先驅<br />\n佢早期當紅嗰時已經開始做緊啲打破香港樂壇框框嘅事<br />\n雨傘之後做咗獨立歌手就更加多"},{"pid":"59646c7bc7648fb0608ff8d78f64826f8a3e9043","tid":1916033,"uid":89394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T14:31:35.000Z","msg":"日媒⋯居然無周庭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"573e4a21e1df3e614c886016ad631d3c17b15e88","tid":1916033,"uid":250721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"59646c7bc7648fb0608ff8d78f64826f8a3e9043","tid":1916033,"uid":89394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T14:31:35.000Z","msg":"日媒⋯居然無周庭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T14:37:01.000Z","msg":"真，點解冇聖女貞德<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}